#circuitbreakersg day 49

Oh my god, Chicken Curry with potatoes🥘 So good! (🐔 delivery from Porkchick- check out their fb page)

This time we pair it with Roti prata, Gardenia’s Ciabatta and Mission’s Pita bread. Pita is the best pairing in my opinion.

Stir-fry Broccoli with scallops from @9sseafood 😋

#stayhome #jxeatshome
Curry and potatos sounds delicious with fresh pita 🤤
Love these dishes!!! Broccoli w Scallop & Curry 😋
Love that prata and curry chicken 😍
